---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Eric Qiu's photography archive." path="/about/">
  <section class="prose-page">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>A small archive for photographs that kept following me home.</h1>
    <p>
      This is a personal photography archive by <a href="https://ericqiu.dev" rel="me">Eric Qiu</a>. Some of the images are from far away;
      some are just from looking a little longer than usual.
    </p>
    <p>
      The edit is loose on purpose: weather, streets, water, buildings, passing details, and a few frames that do not need much said around
      them.
    </p>
    <p>
      For software work, writing, and contact information, visit <a href="https://ericqiu.dev">ericqiu.dev</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
